全风险，而且在IOS平台，其实是限制热修复的，所以热修复方案需要慎用。Flutter官方原本准备开发CodePush用于热更新，出于安全考虑以及平台限制，也停止开发了。","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/486/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/486/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"menus":[]},"__N_SSG":true}